5550372/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Rectal+cancer%3A+MR+imaging+in+local+staging%E2%80%94is+gadolinium-based+contrast+material+helpful%3F&amp;author=RF+Vliegen&amp;author=GL+Beets&amp;author=MF+von+Meyenfeldt&amp;publication_year=2005&amp;journal=Radiology&amp;pages=179-188&amp;doi=10.1148%2Fradiol.2341031403&amp;pmid=15550372">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></section></div><div class="core-collateral" role="dialog" aria-modal="true"><div id="core-collateral-info" data-active-pane="false"><header><h2><i class="icon-info" aria-hidden="true"></i>Information &amp; Authors</h2></header><section id="tab-information" role="tabpanel"><h3>Information</h3><section class="core-self-citation"><h4>Published In</h4><div class="core-journal-presentation">



        
